flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Prepare ID - uint16_t]
    B --> C[Prepare PAYLOAD - 16 bytes]
    C --> D[Set LEN = 16]
    D --> E[Compute CRC16 over ID + LEN + PAYLOAD]
    E --> F{Output}
    F --> G[Write SOF - 0xAA]
    G --> H[Write ID - high, low]
H --> I[Write LEN - 0x10]
I --> J[Write PAYLOAD - 16 bytes]
J --> K[Write CRC - high, low]
K --> L[Write EOF - 0x55]
L --> M[Done]
